title: Best and Worst Free Agent Signings
itunes:title: Best and Worst Free Agent Signings
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus and Gregg Rosenthal are joined by ESPN's Bill Barnwell to bring you all of the latest news in the NFL starting with the Colts bringing back Ty Hilton (9:16), the Giants signing Adoree Jackson (12:15) and Philly's new quarterback (23:00). We hit eight o'clock delight to discuss some more signings before discussing the best and worst free agency signings (35:26).
